"a DNS reverse zone (see :ref:`networks-dns`) assigned to the selected "
"network object (see :ref:`network-objects`), a host record and/or pointer"
" record is automatically created for the host. If there is a DHCP service"
" configured for the network object and a MAC address is configured, a "
"DHCP host entry is created (see :ref:`module-dhcp-dhcp`)."
